{"thag2.44:0.1":"Theragatha 2.44 ","thag2.44:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.44:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.44:0.4":"Mogharajattheragatha ","thag2.44:1.1":"“Chavipapaka cittabhaddaka, ","thag2.44:1.2":"Mogharaja satatam samahito; ","thag2.44:1.3":"Hemantikasitakalarattiyo, ","thag2.44:1.4":"Bhikkhu tvamsi katham karissasi”. ","thag2.44:2.1":"“Sampannasassa magadha, ","thag2.44:2.2":"kevala iti me sutam; ","thag2.44:2.3":"Palalacchannako seyyam, ","thag2.44:2.4":"yathanne sukhajivino”ti. ","thag2.44:2.5":"… Mogharaja thero …. "}